entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`id` TEXT NOT NULL, `day_of_week` TEXT NOT NULL, `gregorian_day` INTEGER NOT NULL, `gregorian_month` INTEGER NOT NULL, `gregorian_year` INTEGER NOT NULL, `last_updated` TEXT NOT NULL, `title` TEXT NOT NULL, `week` TEXT NOT NULL, `liturgical_info` TEXT NOT NULL, `fasting_info` TEXT NOT NULL, `readings` TEXT NOT NULL, `saints` TEXT NOT NULL, `search_text` TEXT NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`id`))

contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_calendar_days_fts_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `calendar_days` BEGIN DELETE FROM `calendar_days_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_calendar_days_fts_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `calendar_days` BEGIN DELETE FROM `calendar_days_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_calendar_days_fts_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `calendar_days` BEGIN INSERT INTO `calendar_days_fts`(`docid`, `search_text`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`search_text`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_calendar_days_fts_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `calendar_days` BEGIN INSERT INTO `calendar_days_fts`(`docid`, `search_text`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`search_text`); END
entities.createSql: CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` USING FTS4(`search_text` TEXT NOT NULL, content=`calendar_days`)
